Upgrading from version 2.6.x to 2.8.0

1. install SQL-Ledger over top
   # cd /usr/local
   # tar zxvf sql-ledger-2.8.0.tar.gz

2. fix permissions
   # chown -hR nobody:nogroup *
   # chmod 711 templates users css spool

Note: replace nobody:nogroup with your web server user and group

3. copy the following templates from the templates directory to
   your private directory

   Default-credit_invoice.html
   Default-credit_invoice.tex
   Default-credit_note.html
   Default-credit_note.tex
   Default-debit_invoice.html
   Default-debit_invoice.tex
   Default-debit_note.html
   Default-debit_note.tex

   remove the Default- prefix
   
4. log in

5. Go to System -> Defaults and enter your company name

